  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators here propose to perform a prospective randomized intervention trial in
      post-menopausal women to investigate the endocrine network, which contributes to the changes
      in skeletal muscle mass during weight loss.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
